prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Sculpture Lantern Slide Collection, Arts Library, Yale University

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Collection consists of black and white glass lantern slides of sculpture.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Arranged alphabetically by nationality individual artist name. Sub-divided primarily by location of the work. Some sections are preceded by an Anonymous grouping arranged chronologically.
